{"tid":455494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麥當勞員工的警告： 唔好食魚柳包！","createTime":"2017-11-02T06:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T06:59:17.000Z","uid":70985,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6034dd3c477923bf9a5d22f6eb2f7a2104c3b5f8","tid":455494,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"麥當勞快餐店有甚麼食物是「不可點」？有自稱是麥當勞前員工的外國網民，在社交網Reddit爆料指魚柳包就是其中一款，原因是它較漢堡包和薯條不受歡迎，故魚柳包都不是新鮮即製。<br />\n<br />\n有網民指魚柳包較少人點，故分配給顧客的魚柳包有機會已放置了很久，「可能放在加熱櫃數小時」。他呼籲顧客要求即製，以確保食物不會是凍。<br />\n另有自稱三年前曾在麥當勞打工的網民也指，魚柳包「可以想像到不新鮮」。不過有人表示不介意魚柳包不新鮮和即叫即製，「因我不認為那本身與新鮮扯得上關係」。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171101/57399605\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F57399605&d=2qj4hJ%2F0yb%2FUxPeMlBt47Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=2da14a39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171101%2F57399605&h=abebe1a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20171101/57399605</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老麥會有新鮮整嘅野咩？"},{"pid":"160bcb15b75e52f2ea7e658946c4f94debf37e5b","tid":455494,"uid":41317,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:41:44.000Z","msg":"外國我唔知<br />\n但係香港魚柳包好好賣<br />\n好賣到1,2日已經炸到缸油豉油咁嘅色"},{"pid":"eeed5dbd8d63741e50c519d63d602c4109f721f5","tid":455494,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:43:21.000Z","msg":"中信金拱門"},{"pid":"601e429c42b3cf9cb5179e01d11dd4ea0c9f60d6","tid":455494,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:47:07.000Z","msg":"味道唔差喎"},{"pid":"09c841340460e0c9ac06763bc8c1455c2c2b2892","tid":455494,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"香港好多人叫"},{"pid":"d07410bd580f5f9029113078af2c038d3b1b947d","tid":455494,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"朝早食 好新鮮 真係外脆內軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ffb7ebff5334bcaa0106949d83602e3438fe44","tid":455494,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"好似話漢堡包果隻扒最污糟"},{"pid":"18c33d3cd093ed9790e2ae36c3abb6c86e3a6dc1","tid":455494,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中信金拱門</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa94df02295ca70adf4cc07f35bee044c48885a","tid":455494,"uid":117150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似話漢堡包果隻扒最污糟</blockquote><br />\n10:1擺耐左好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}